name: Tupac Shakur Typography Portrait Print
description:
RIP Tupac Shakur
Composed of my favorite 2pac track titles, album titles, and also information about the man. It was a struggle trying to get everything as legible as possible. 2pac fans should be able to make out most of it. 
(20) Limited 1st Prints of each size/colored (signed & numbered). 
Available in 24x20.5, 28x24 or 41x36 print on 20lb paper. 
Also available in a 16x20 canvas print. 
*Each of the (20) colored portraits will vary in color combinations and differ from each other.
(Orders for colored prints will be taken 3 at a time and may take 2 weeks before delivery.)

name: Tyler the Creator Print
description:
A friend recommended I give Tyler the Creator a listen and do a print. His idea of what the print should be was... on a different plane of explicit thought. I heard some mixtapes along with the goblin album and thought.."Damn...kids only 19 and producing some cool shit." I decided to keep a bit of "explicit-ness" to it and do a print.
(50) Limited 1st Prints of each size (signed and numbered).
Available in 24x16.5, 35x24 or 53x36 size print on 20lb. paper.
